{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, creating dynamic AI systems that collaborate with human agents in real-time can enhance customer service.",
    "Continuous improvement through iterative learning, based on feedback from complex interactions, is essential for maintaining high standards of customer service.",
    "AI systems in customer service are often designed for efficiency, which can sometimes sacrifice personalization.",
    "Automated responses and standardized processes can handle high volumes of inquiries quickly but may not provide the individualized attention that customers appreciate.",
    "This trade-off can make customers feel undervalued and dissatisfied as they miss the personalized interactions that human agents typically offer."
  ]
}